(PAYMENT POLICY) Tj
T*
(Last updated: January 2025) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(OVERVIEW) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This document explains the payment methods we accept, how transactions are processed,) Tj
T*
(what happens when a payment fails, how we handle disputes and chargebacks, and how we) Tj
T*
(protect your financial information.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(1. ACCEPTED PAYMENT METHODS) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1.1 Credit and Debit Cards) Tj
T*
(We accept all major credit and debit cards including:) Tj
T*
(- Visa) Tj
T*
(- Mastercard) Tj
T*
(- American Express) Tj
T*
(- Discover) Tj
T*
(- Diners Club \(select regions\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Your card is charged at the time of order placement for in-stock items. For pre-) Tj
T*
(orders and back-ordered items, your card is charged when the item ships.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1.2 Digital Wallets) Tj
T*
(- Apple Pay: available on Safari and the iOS app) Tj
T*
(- Google Pay: available on Chrome and the Android app) Tj
T*
(- PayPal: log into your PayPal account at checkout to pay with your PayPal balance,) Tj
T*
(linked bank, or PayPal credit) Tj
T*
(- Shop Pay: fast one-tap checkout with stored payment details) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1.3 Buy Now, Pay Later \(BNPL\)) Tj
T*
(We partner with the following BNPL providers:) Tj
T*
(- Klarna: split into 4 interest-free payments, or flexible monthly financing) Tj
T*
(- Afterpay: split into 4 fortnightly interest-free installments) Tj
T*
(- Affirm: monthly payment plans from 3 to 36 months \(subject to credit approval\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(BNPL options appear at checkout for eligible orders. Minimum order amounts apply.) Tj
T*
(BNPL is subject to approval by the respective provider. Refunds on BNPL orders are) Tj
T*
(handled in coordination with the provider ? credits are applied to your BNPL) Tj
T*
(installment plan, which may affect your payment schedule.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1.4 Gift Cards and Store Credit) Tj
T*
(Gift cards and store credit can be applied at checkout. Multiple gift cards can be) Tj
T*
(combined. Gift cards cannot be applied to subscription purchases.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1.5 Bank Transfer \(ACH\)) Tj
ET
