(ACH transfers are available for Business plan customers and orders over $500. ACH) Tj
T*
(payments take 3 to 5 business days to clear. Orders paid by ACH are held until) Tj
T*
(payment clears before shipping.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1.6 Cryptocurrencies) Tj
T*
(We currently do not accept cryptocurrency payments.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(2. CURRENCY AND INTERNATIONAL PAYMENTS) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(2.1 Base Currency) Tj
T*
(All prices are displayed and charged in US Dollars \(USD\) by default.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(2.2 Local Currency Display) Tj
T*
(Customers browsing from outside the United States can select their local currency for) Tj
T*
(price display using the currency selector in the website header. Displayed local) Tj
T*
(currency prices are estimates based on live exchange rates. Your card or payment) Tj
T*
(provider will handle the final conversion and may apply a foreign transaction fee.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(2.3 Foreign Transaction Fees) Tj
T*
(We do not charge foreign transaction fees. However, your bank or card issuer may) Tj
T*
(charge one \(typically 1% to 3%\). Check with your financial institution if this is a) Tj
T*
(concern.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(3. PAYMENT SECURITY) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3.1 PCI DSS Compliance) Tj
T*
(We are fully compliant with Payment Card Industry Data Security Standard \(PCI DSS\)) Tj
T*
(Level 1, the highest certification level. We do not store your full card number on) Tj
T*
(our servers ? card data is tokenized and handled by our certified payment processor.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3.2 Secure Checkout) Tj
T*
(All payment pages use TLS 1.2 or higher encryption \(indicated by the padlock icon in) Tj
T*
(your browser\). Never enter payment details on a page without HTTPS.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3.3 Two-Factor Authentication for High-Value Orders) Tj
T*
(Orders above $300 may trigger an additional authentication step \(3D Secure / Verified) Tj
T*
(by Visa / Mastercard SecureCode\). You may receive an SMS code or be redirected to) Tj
T*
(your bank's authentication page. This is normal and protects you from unauthorized) Tj
T*
(use of your card.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3.4 Fraud Detection) Tj
T*
(Our automated fraud detection system analyzes orders in real time. Orders flagged for) Tj
T*
(review may be held for up to 24 hours while we verify the transaction. We may contact) Tj
T*
(you by phone or email for verification. You are not charged for orders held for) Tj
T*
(review until the order is confirmed.) Tj
ET
endstream
