(6.3 Subscription Invoices) Tj
T*
(Subscription billing receipts are sent automatically after each renewal. Historical) Tj
T*
(subscription invoices are available in Account > Billing History.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(7. PAYMENT DISPUTES AND CHARGEBACKS) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(7.1 Resolve Issues With Us First) Tj
T*
(Before disputing a charge with your bank, please contact our support team. Most) Tj
T*
(billing issues are resolved faster directly with us than through the chargeback) Tj
T*
(process. You can reach us at billing@shopexample.com.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(7.2 Unauthorized Charges) Tj
T*
(If you see a charge from us that you did not authorize, contact us immediately at) Tj
T*
(security@shopexample.com. We will investigate and refund unauthorized charges) Tj
T*
(confirmed to be fraudulent within 5 business days.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(7.3 Chargeback Process) Tj
T*
(If you initiate a chargeback \(dispute the charge with your card issuer\), we will) Tj
T*
(receive a notification and respond to the dispute with the relevant order and) Tj
T*
(delivery documentation. Initiating a chargeback while an order is in transit or a) Tj
T*
(return is being processed may complicate resolution. We encourage you to work with us) Tj
T*
(directly first.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(7.4 Chargeback Consequences) Tj
T*
(If a chargeback is found to be fraudulent or in bad faith \(e.g., item was received) Tj
T*
(but reported as not received\), we reserve the right to:) Tj
T*
(- Suspend or close the associated account) Tj
T*
(- Flag the account for future order review) Tj
T*
(- Pursue recovery of funds in accordance with applicable law) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(8. PROMOTIONAL CODES AND DISCOUNTS) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(8.1 Applying Promo Codes) Tj
T*
(Enter your promo code in the designated field at checkout. Codes are case-sensitive.) Tj
T*
(Only one promo code can be applied per order \(unless stated otherwise in the) Tj
T*
(promotion terms\). Promo codes cannot be applied retroactively to completed orders.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(8.2 Promo Code Restrictions) Tj
T*
(- Some codes are valid only for specific product categories) Tj
T*
(- Minimum order value requirements may apply) Tj
T*
(- Codes may exclude sale items or subscriptions) Tj
T*
(- Expired codes cannot be reactivated) Tj
T*
() Tj
ET
