T*
(If an item you purchased goes on sale within 7 days of your order date, you may be) Tj
T*
(eligible for a one-time price adjustment credit. Contact support with your order) Tj
T*
(number within 7 days of the sale start. Price adjustments are issued as store credit,) Tj
T*
(not as a refund to your payment method. This applies once per order.) Tj
T*
() Tj
