T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Sales tax is collected for orders delivered to states where we are required to do so) Tj
T*
(by law. The applicable tax rate is calculated based on the delivery address and item) Tj
T*
(type. Tax amounts are displayed at checkout before you confirm payment. If you are a) Tj
T*
(tax-exempt organization, contact billing@shopexample.com before placing your order) Tj
T*
(with your exemption documentation.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(10. CONTACT FOR PAYMENT ISSUES) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Billing inquiries: billing@shopexample.com) Tj
T*
(Unauthorized charges or fraud: security@shopexample.com) Tj
T*
(Phone: 1-800-555-0199 \(Monday to Friday, 9 AM to 6 PM Eastern\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
